data.description: Nestled in a convenient Sparks neighborhood with no HOA, this single-story home offers a comfortable living space with 1,642 square feet. The kitchen has been recently updated, providing a fresh and modern space. Throughout the home, newer flooring adds a clean and contemporary feel. Residents can enjoy the added benefits of solar panels for energy efficiency. The location is ideal, with easy with easy access to local amenities and a park within walking distance for relaxation and outdoor activities. 2 year old carpet and interior paint, 4 year old roof, windows/sliders, updated baths, plantation shutters, honeycomb blinds, & real fireplace. The electrical panel was also replaced 4 years ago. RV access, dog run, easy access to dining, shopping, & schools.
